title: Grateful Dead Live at Fiesta Hall, San Mateo County Fairgrounds on 1981-12-12
venue: Fiesta Hall, San Mateo County Fairgrounds
description:
Set 1

Me And Bobby McGee, Children Of The Eighties, Lucifer's Eyes Of The World, Warriors Of The Sun, Bye Bye Love, Barbara Allen, You Won't Find Me, Heroes Gone, Oh Boy, Lady Di**, The Boxer**

Set 2

Minglewood Blues*, Little Red Rooster*, Deep Elem Blues, Me & My Uncle, Mexicali Blues, Dire Wolf, Cold Rain & Snow, Around & Around*, One More Saturday Night, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue***

*With Matt Kelley,** Without Jerry, ***With Joan Baez, without Jerry & Brent
